data.description: *SELLER MOTIVATED* SUPER LOW HOA! Another immaculate Property Just Listed in Fort Myers!Enjoy this high ceiling renovated home with tons of upgrades in the well known Wrinkle Road Corridor of Fort Myers. This home is located near major hospitals, shops and NEAR THE BEACH!!  Just a short drive to FMB, Sanibel and Captiva. This home features a 3BR+den or office & 2 BA, a beautifully renovated kitchen, with upgraded cabinets and granite  counter tops, wine cooler, a large island, new flooring, all brand new stainless steel smart appliances and a 90 degree sliding glass door for maximum natural light. Enjoy the serenity of the owners suite with beautiful lighting, crown molding, his/hers walk in closets, double sinks in the bathroom, shower and a tub to unwind. Enjoy the Florida lifestyle on the raised extended deck in the backyard for a beautiful view of the Florida sunshine. Home is equipped with storm smart shutters, screened lanai, upgraded outdoor outlets, brand new window blinds . The community pool is steps away from the house, so enjoy the pool without the maintenance hustle!!
